processVariable.name: instancesStatuses
dataSeriesP

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select TM.MONITOR_NAME || ' - ' || TM.MONITOR_SEQ as monitor, trunc(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'hh24') + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'mi')/(<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>*1))*(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>))/24/60 as name, TRUNC(avg(TMR.RESPONSE_TIME), 3) as value from TDSH_MONITOR_RESULTS TMR, TDSH_MONITORS TM where TM.MONITOR_SEQ = TMR.MONITOR_SEQ <# if (tw.local.monitorType == 99) { } else {#> and TM.MONITOR_TYPE_ID = <#= tw.local.monitorType #> <# } #> and TMR.CHECK_DATETIME > SYSDATE - <#=tw.local.minutesBack#>/1440 group by TM.MONITOR_NAME || ' - ' || TM.MONITOR_SEQ , trunc(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'hh24') + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'mi')/(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>))*(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>))/24/60 order by monitor

tw.local.sqlStatement select TM.MONITOR_NAME || ' - ' || TM.MONITOR_SEQ as monitor, trunc(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'hh24') + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'mi')/(<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>*1))*(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>)) MINUTES as name, TRUNC(avg(TMR.RESPONSE_TIME), 3) as value from TDSH_MONITOR_RESULTS TMR, TDSH_MONITORS TM where TM.MONITOR_SEQ = TMR.MONITOR_SEQ <# if (tw.local.monitorType == 99) { } else {#> and TM.MONITOR_TYPE_ID = <#= tw.local.monitorType #> <# } #> and TMR.CHECK_DATETIME > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - <#=tw.local.minutesBack#> MINUTES group by TM.MONITOR_NAME || ' - ' || TM.MONITOR_SEQ , trunc(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'hh24') + (trunc(to_char(TMR.CHECK_DATETIME,'mi')/(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>))*(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>)) MINUTES order by monitor

tw.local.sqlStatement select CONCAT(TM.MONITOR_NAME, TM.MONITOR_SEQ) as monitor, CONCAT(TM.MONITOR_NAME, TM.MONITOR_SEQ) , DATEADD(mi, (datepart(minute, TMR.CHECK_DATETIME)/(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>))*(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>), DATEADD(hour, DATEDIFF(hour, 0, TMR.CHECK_DATETIME), 0))
as name, avg(TMR.RESPONSE_TIME) as value from TDSH_MONITOR_RESULTS TMR, TDSH_MONITORS TM where TM.MONITOR_SEQ = TMR.MONITOR_SEQ <# if (tw.local.monitorType == 99) { } else {#> and TM.MONITOR_TYPE_ID = <#= tw.local.monitorType #> <# } #> and TMR.CHECK_DATETIME > DATEADD(mi, - <#=tw.local.minutesBack#>, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) group by CONCAT(TM.MONITOR_NAME, TM.MONITOR_SEQ) , DATEADD(mi, (datepart(minute, TMR.CHECK_DATETIME)/(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>))*(1*<#=tw.local.perMinutes#>), DATEADD(hour, DATEDIFF(hour, 0, TMR.CHECK_DATETIME), 0)) order by monitor
